-----------------------------
 COMP SUPERSCALAR FRAMEWORK
-----------------------------

* COMP Superscalar framework packages can be found on builders/packages/ directory.

* COMPSs Documentation (doc/):

  * The COMP Superscalar installation guide:
    - installation-guide.html

  * The COMP Superscalar manual:
    - compss-manual.pdf

-------------------------
 BUILDING THE FRAMEWORK
-------------------------

* Build command: 
      
     $ cd compss; mvn package

  (IMPORTANT: Requires Maven 3.0.x version)


* Building packages on Debian based machine:

  In order to be able to build Debian & Red-Hat packages the following packages should be installed:

    - sudo apt-get install build-essential autoconf automake autotools-dev\ 
           dh-make debhelper devscripts fakeroot xutils lintian pbuilder rpm

* Building packages on Red-Hat based machine:

  In order to be able to build Debian & Red-Hat packages the following packages should be installed:
    - yast2 -i deb

* Prepare Debian & Red-Hat packages:

     - Both:
	$ cd builders/; ./buildall

     - Only Debian:
         $ cd builders/specs/deb/; ./builddeb

     - Only Red-Hat:
         $ cd builders/specs/rpm/; ./buildrpm


